service: demoexpressjs-lambda

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: ap-south-1
  memorySize: 256
  timeout: 10

functions:
  contacts:
    handler: handlers/contactHandler.handler
    package:
      individually: true
      include:
        - handlers/contactHandler.js
        - controllers/contactController.js
        - models/contactModel.js
      exclude:
        - controllers/**
        - models/**
    events:
      - http:
          path: api/contacts/{proxy+}
          method: ANY
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: api/contacts
          method: ANY
          cors: true

package:
  individually: true
  exclude:
    - tests/**
    - docs/**
    - .git/**
    - "*.md"
